re susceptible to these attacks. We report success\nrates up to 92.56% for floating point attacks on DP-SGD, and up to 99.65% for\nend-to-end timing attacks on private sum protected with discrete Laplace.\nFinally, we evaluate and suggest partial mitigations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Dec 2021 02:57:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 04:45:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 05:21:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-16"}
