 intermediate-mass black hole in Nikhuli, and suggestive of a black\nhole supply mechanism for bulgeless late-type galaxies. We may potentially be\nwitnessing black hole seeding by capture and sinking, with a nuclear star\ncluster the delivery vehicle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Dec 2021 03:41:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-20"}
