f intelligent transportation\nsystems will be able to take a step towards its comprehensive roll-out.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Dec 2021 15:49:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Dec 2021 15:22:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Feb 2022 15:21:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 25 Aug 2022 14:01:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-26"}
